description: The An Family first started serving Garlic Noodles 41 years ago, when we opened our first restaurant, Thanh Long, in 1971. Because the noodles have been such a big hit, we've decided to take the secret kitchen dish to the streets with the An the Go Food truck. Check out our great Lemongrass Chicken, Five-Spice Pork, Vegetable Stir-Fry and more!To learn about the secret kitchen and how even Oprah can't get a peek, check out An the Go's article on the Roaming Hunger blog here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/8851/garlic-noodles-we-cant-get-enough-of
name: An The Go
